                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;10947  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;10948  void watchdog_enable (void) 
009c72  4959              LDR      r1,|L2.40408|
;;;10949  {
;;;10950  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;
009c74  05c8              LSLS     r0,r1,#23

;;;10951  LPC_WDT->WDCLKSEL=0;

;;;10952  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;
009c7c  2103              MOVS     r1,#3
009c7e  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;10953  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;

009c82  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10954  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

009c86  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10955  }
009c88  4770              BX       lr
;;;10956  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;10957  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;10958  void watchdog_reset (void) 
009c8a  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
;;;10959  {
;;;10960  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009c8c  0748              LSLS     r0,r1,#29

;;;10961  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

;;;10962  }
009c94  4770              BX       lr
;;;10963  
                          ENDP

                  SysTick_Handler PROC
;;;10969  //***********************************************
;;;10970  void SysTick_Handler (void) 	 /* SysTick Interrupt Handler (1ms)    */

;;;10971  {
;;;10972  //sys_plazma++;
;;;10973  b2000Hz=1;

;;;10979  	}
;;;10980  
;;;10981  if(++t0cnt4>=2)

                  |L2.40170|

;;;10990  if(modbus_timeout_cnt<modbusTimeoutInMills)

;;;10992  	modbus_timeout_cnt++;

;;;10994  		{
